lead_paragraph: Sean McMahon is to start at number eight in place of the injured David Pocock in the only change to Australia's starting lineup for the Rugby Championship tussle against South Africa in Pretoria on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Rugby-McMahon Replaces Pocock for Wallabies Versus Springboks
